, 984.8, 1023.6]}, {"text": "405.7", "bbox": [1005.6, 1002.7, 1052.5, 1023.6]}, {"text": "In December 2007, we issued an aggregate of $500 million principal amount of our 5.65% notes due 2017", "bbox": [185.5, 1061.0, 1094.2, 1081.8]}, {"text": "and 6.25% debentures due 2037. The debt offering yielded approximately $493.5 million of proceeds, which", "bbox": [143.8, 1086.0, 1094.2, 1106.8]}, {"text": "were used to repay at maturity our 6.15% notes due January 15, 2008 and for general corporate purposes.", "bbox": [143.8, 1111.0, 1022.5, 1131.8]}, {"text": "We issued an aggregate of $800 million principal amount of our 6.15% notes, 6.70% debentures and 5.20%", "bbox": [185.5, 1156.7, 1094.2, 1177.6]}, {"text": "debentures in January 1998. The debt offering yielded approximately $750.0 million of proceeds. We issued the", "bbox": [143.8, 1181.7, 1094.1, 1202.6]}, {"text": "5.20% debentures at a discount, and the 6.15% notes and 6.70% debentures at par.", "bbox": [143.8, 1206.7, 831.2, 1227.6]}, {"text": "In September 2002, we entered into an interest rate swap contract (the Swap) that effectively converted our", "bbox": [185.5, 1252.5, 1094.2, 1273.3]}, {"text": "$350.0 million aggregate principal amount of 6.15% notes, payable in 2008, to floating rate debt based on", "bbox": [143.8, 1277.5, 1094.2, 1298.3]}, {"text": "six-month LIBOR. The floating rate was 7.80 percent at September 30, 2007. As permitted by SFAS No. 133,", "bbox": [143.8, 1302.5, 1094.2, 1323.3]}, {"text": "Accounting for Derivative Instruments and Hedging Activities (SFAS 133), as amended, we designated the Swap", "bbox": [143.8, 1327.3, 1094.2, 1348.3]}, {"text": "as a fair value hedge. Accordingly, the fair value of the Swap was recorded in other liabilities on the", "bbox": [143.8, 1352.5, 1094.1, 1373.4]}, {"text": "Consolidated Balance Sheet with a corresponding adjustment to the carrying value of the underlying debt at", "bbox": [143.8, 1377.5, 1094.1, 1398.4]}, {"text": "September 30, 2007. The fair value of the Swap, based upon quoted market prices for contracts with similar", "bbox": [143.8, 1402.5, 1093.9, 1423.4]}, {"text": "maturities, was a liability of $1.8 million at September 30, 2007. The Swap matured on January 15, 2008.", "bbox": [143.8, 1427.5, 1025.6, 1448.4]}, {"text": "53", "bbox": [608.6, 1478.3, 629.4, 1499.1]}]}